header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - 1ST ROUND

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Ban Lammers takes the pass from Tadric Jackson and hammers home an uncontested slam.
videos.headline: Lammers throws down 2-handed jam

videos.description: Two quick passes by the Eagles lead to Nik Popovic being wide open in the lane for a dunk.
videos.headline: BC's passing leads to Popovic jam

videos.description: Boston College head coach Jim Christian says that his team needs to stay patient and keep playing solid defense in the 2nd half against Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Patience, defense are keys for BC in 2nd half

videos.description: Boston College's Ky Bowman drives and hits contested lay-in off the glass.
videos.headline: Bowman hits impressive left layup

videos.description: Brandon Alston knocks down a 3-pointer for Georgia Tech which is followed by Tadric Jackson stealing the inbounds pass and slamming it home.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Jackson throws it down after big 3
